snippet.title: Amber Heard Visits Domestic Abuse Psychologist
snippet.description:
Wednesday, June 8, 2016 - Amber Heard visited the home of clinical psychologist Connell Cowan on Wednesday, as her domestic abuse accusations against Johnny Depp make headlines.  The actress got dressed up in a wide-brimmed hat and wide-legged jeans with mirrored sunglasses, for a meeting with the author of “Smart Women, Foolish Choices,” a book about why women consistently choose the wrong men and how to stop.
